<Body>
	<Title>日本旅馆饭菜导致72名观光客集体食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年2月1日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1">据<Participant sid="s1">中新网</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">2月1日</Time>援引日本共同社<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2">日本宫城县政府</Participant><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">1日</Time><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Location lid="l3">该县气仙沼市“大岛观光旅馆 丸荣”</Location>的<Participant sid="s3">72名客人</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>上吐下泻等<Object oid="o3">食物中毒症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e4">其中<Participant sid="s4">9人</Participant>经<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">检测</Denoter>查出诺罗病毒</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">县政府</Participant>已<Denoter did="d5" type="statement">命令</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">旅馆</Participant><Time tid="t6" type="timeInterval">自1日起</Time><Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">停业</Denoter><Time tid="t6" type="timeInterval">3天</Time></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
     
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e7">据<Participant sid="s7">该县政府</Participant><Denoter did="d7" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8">这<Participant sid="s8">72人</Participant>是来自山形县的团体观光客，<Time tid="t8" type="timeInterval">上月20日起</Time><Denoter did="d8" type="operation">入住</Denoter><Location lid="l8">该旅馆</Location></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">宫城县政府</Participant>从症状<Denoter did="d9" type="operation">分析</Denoter>认定这是一次集体食物中毒事件</Event>，原因是<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">20日</Time><Participant sid="s10">旅馆</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="operation">提供</Denoter>的<Object oid="o10">晚饭</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>据说这些人症状较轻，都在康复之中。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		</Content>
